      • login

        public boolean login()
        Logs user into WatCard site by initiating a POST request containing a __RequestVerificationToken and user account details. Uses a WatSession to store cookies and verification token.
        Returns:
        true if login is successful, otherwise it throws an exception.

      • getLastDaysTransactions

        public List<WatTransaction> getLastDaysTransactions(int days,
                                                    boolean exact)
        Returns a list of all transactions completed within a given amount of days from now.
        Parameters:
        days - number of days
        exact - true, meaning only transactions made within last begin days (precise to the second) from now false, meaning transactions made from 0:00:00 of begin to now.
        Returns:
        a list of WatTransactions completed within the last begin days
